location.fullValue: Lucerne Lakes Homes Village I 3rd Addition

data.description: This well-built 2BR/2BA, 1 car garage CBS single-family home comes with numerous recent upgrades! Revel in fresh carpeting throughout all bedrooms, modernized appliances, an investment of over $15,000 in impact windows and doors, a primary suite with an attached bath and spacious walk-in closet, a generously-sized screened patio, and much more. Additional upgrades encompass a newer A/C system, a newly installed Wi-Fi-enabled garage door, updated light fixtures, a new electrical panel, a recent water heater, and a new disposal. Ideally situated, it is in close proximity to the Lucerne Lakes Swim Club and the Forest Oaks Public Golf Course. Within minutes, you can reach shopping, beaches, dining, and the turnpike, all while benefiting from low HOA fees. Community Pool and more!
